column44:
I'd say that was a tough starting break
for any other hunter, but in this case,
perhaps it was some odd sort of fate.

Honestly, it's not the sort of thing I would
have ever thought of—Nakago suggested it;
said it might help to keep your spirits up.

column45:
Pour être honnête, je n'y aurais jamais pensé ;
c'était l'idée de Nakago. Il a dit qu'il
espérait que ça te ferait plaisir.

